metadata.name: Crunchy Bones #1
metadata.description: Crunchy Bones is a community driven collection featuring 2000 party-loving, dynamic NFTs. Created by French designer Simon, Crunchy Bones are your personal companion and will become your Metaverse persona, so get a hold of a Crunchy Bone which you feel represents you. Visit [crunchybones.io](https://www.crunchybones.io/) for more details.
